13:45.366 --> 13:47.243
but it doesn't mean that
       there aren't solutions.

13:49.119 --> 13:51.705
We have a responsibility
            to detect them.

13:51.747 --> 13:53.332
The question becomes:

13:53.374 --> 13:56.544
What type of technology
         do you need to do so?

